Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.21,0:01:24.61,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Aruki dasou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:43.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because of you guys, we didn't have\ntime to eat anything, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:48.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mm, this goes down pretty smooth, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.44,0:01:49.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H181A0D&\bord0\shad0\pos(294,93)\frz339.054}The Island Nearest to Paradise
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.44,0:01:49.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H181A0D&\shad0\bord0\pos(307,212)\frz342.258}August 11, 2006, 11:00 am
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:01:53.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I was thinking there was\nno other possible way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.98,0:01:55.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So was I.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.44,0:02:01.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When a person gets caught up in one notion,\nhe becomes unable to think of anything else,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:07.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,even though, in fact, another way of resolving\nthings is often right before his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:17.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we hadn't had that damned campfire,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:21.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we might have dragged ourselves\nright up there and done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.97,0:02:23.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.07,0:02:26.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have to be grateful to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.69,0:02:43.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:48.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's good you didn't die, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:33.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:38.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:43.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:46.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:52.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was more scared than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:33.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why is it that at times like this\NI'm not plagued by lethargy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:37.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd like to just sleep,\nwithout thinking about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:04:59.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:06.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:08.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He looks like he's from an inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:12.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Would you be the group from the\N"Island Nearest to Paradise" Off Meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:16.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How does he know about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.11,0:05:18.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I put a call in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:21.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're all tired, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:24.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can take a hot spring bath and\nrelax a bit before we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:27.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jogasaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:29.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, now, right this way please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:32.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall we take him up on this offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:34.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, come along, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:48.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? No, I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.31,0:05:50.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really? You're not with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:53.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jogasaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:56.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll be there as soon as I return the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:14.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your names and addresses, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:21.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:23.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H563637&\shad0\bord0\frx20\fry0\move(198,43,198,37,0,2589)}Guest Register
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:40.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was an unbelievable day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:41.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:46.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At this time yesterday, we'd all given up hope\nabout everything in this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:51.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and now we're here soaking in a hot spring, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:07:00.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you the ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:02.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The fools who were going to cast away your lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:06.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Fools," you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:07.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:16.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Selfishly throwing away the life his parents\ngave him is something a fool does.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:21.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you actually were dead now,\nyou'd be beyond all salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:22.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:26.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Things are a little better anyway,\nsince you came back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:32.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you guys hadn't come back safely,\nwhat do you think would've happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:38.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The marina staff would all have been\nsent out as search crews.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:43.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In the worst case, the people from the fisheries\ncooperative might have gotten dragged in too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:49.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The inns hereabouts would've fallen behind\nin their work with all the inquiries and whatnot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:53.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If your bodies had washed up,\nthat would've been big news too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:58.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Worst case, if they'd drifted up near the inns, it'd have\nan impact on the lodge businesses here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:02.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It'd be huge trouble all around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:08.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well? Now do you see the idiocy of fools who would\nthrow away their lives and cause trouble to others
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:11.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,just because of their own situations?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:17.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you do understand, then don't ever\nthink up anything so stupid again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:24.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is a warning from somebody who\nwas a fool himself long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:34.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hana-Hana's running late, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:38.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Women's baths take a long time, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:41.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's nothing for it. Shall we start without her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:46.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? I'm sure that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.62,0:08:48.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:51.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I had that young man Jogasaki go get it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:56.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were out for a drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:04.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just a bit, it's such a nice car. I couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:08.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Women really are tougher than men.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:16.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mr. Nomura, Mr. Kusano,\nmembers of your family are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:20.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H182830&\bord0\shad0\fnSegoe Script\pos(306,43)}Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:22.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H182830&\bord0\shad0\fnSegoe Script\pos(360,93)}Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:29.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H182830&\bord0\shad0\fnSegoe Script\fscx190\fscy172.5\pos(191,261)}Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:28.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hidehito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:37.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about the clinic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:40.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just leave it to your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:44.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All this because you can't become a doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:49.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:53.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:58.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:10:00.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How could you do something so stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:04.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The fault is all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:08.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no excuse for what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:11.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you! Dragging our son into this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop it, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:15.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:18.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's because I'm such a wimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.73,0:10:47.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To have my mother cry at me like that is too much.\NI got worn out and escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:54.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Coming from me, it doesn't mean much,\nbut it is wrong to want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:11:02.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After all this, I talked to my mother for the first time\nin a long time, and I finally understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:07.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As long as there's someone who'll grieve,\nit's wrong to want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:14.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato, this is for you, if you're interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:17.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.21,0:11:22.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a free pass to "Ultimate Fantasy,"\nan online game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:27.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you type in this number,\nyou can play for the first month for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:31.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're hikikomori, right, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:37.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A person I met online is also hikikomori,\nand he's making a ton of money off of this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:40.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? Off of a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:41.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:46.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He does R.M.T.: "Real Money Trading."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:52.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He trades items and gold he acquires\nin the game for real money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:53.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Amazing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:55.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:58.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With this, even if you're shut inside your house,\nyou can earn money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:12:01.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's perfect for you, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:04.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'"Vina Teelo"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:06.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you, I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:08.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See you in Vina Teelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:11.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:21.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now you can't die at least\nuntil you meet him inside the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:26.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hidehito! Hidehito!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:30.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going to head out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:39.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We probably won't meet again, but take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:41.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:44.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hidehito, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:47.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm over here. Don't yell like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're back, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:05.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's get going soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:06.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:11.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh, are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:12.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:15.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yamazaki and the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:19.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yamazaki said he had something important to do;
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:21.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he left a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:23.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something important to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:30.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HF56C72&\3c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\pos(124,99)}Sample!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:31.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HF56C72&\3c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\move(124,99,124,292,0,1171)}Sample!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:30.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:33.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you charge 3,000 yen for a trial version?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:35.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is he crazy or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:40.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, he's saying the Comic Stall\nis more important than I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:43.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And about that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:44.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:48.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She just vanished at some point;\NI think she probably went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:52.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wasn't really concerned about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:57.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.03,0:14:02.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Won't you ride back in my car?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:03.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:10.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, I'm in the mood to go home by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:11.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:15.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, once things settle down, let's get together\nin Tokyo to eat or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:17.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:19.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:24.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:31.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry I got you caught up\nin this kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:39.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all right. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:46.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wish you happiness, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:14.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll give you a ride to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:16.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks.
