Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:33.82,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\c&HED9512&\3c&HFFFFED&\bord1.5\4c&H8E8E8E&}Youkoso... Hitoribocchi\N{\c&HFFD367&}Welcome... loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:31.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:34.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:40.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mom told me to come meet you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:43.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She said let's all give it another try.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:34.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H0A1F43&\fnSegoe Script\fscx141.25\fscy133.75\frz40.779\move(140,110,136,92,0,2632)}Misaki Nakahara
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:39.59,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\c&HED9512&\3c&HFFFFED&\bord1.5\4c&H8E8E8E&}Hitoribocchi\N{\c&HFFD367&}Loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:48.57,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\c&HED9512&\3c&HFFFFED&\bord1.5\4c&H8E8E8E&}Hitoribocchi\N{\c&HFFD367&}Loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:57.31,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\c&HED9512&\3c&HFFFFED&\bord1.5\4c&H8E8E8E&}Hitoribocchi\N{\c&HFFD367&}Loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:09.35,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\c&HED9512&\3c&HFFFFED&\bord1.5\4c&H8E8E8E&}Hitoribocchi\N{\c&HFFD367&}Loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:52.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're hikikomori, more pathetic than a stray dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:56.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...so much more of a throwaway\nhunk of refuse than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:04.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So... You can't die! Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:09.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't get her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:24.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you alive, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:38.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it, I didn't think the Comic Stall\ncustomers would all be jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.42,0:17:41.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Learn to read things' auras!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:45.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't they even realize that once it's completed\nit's going to be a big-name item?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:49.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What hurt us is that we didn't get\nto go on the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:52.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Games weren't the main items today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:54.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's your fault, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:57.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't care how much you despaired\nabout your hikikomori life;
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:18:00.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,there was no reason to stir up so much crap\non the day of Comic Stall!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:05.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The idiots in my class are giving me\ncold glares too; I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:12.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H011B34&\bord0\shad0\fnSegoe Script\frz16.447\move(229,147,104,147,0,4466)}I'll be waiting\nat the usual place,\nat the usual time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.45,0:18:15.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting at the usual place, at the usual time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:14.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H011B34&\bord0\shad0\fnSegoe Script\fscx270\fscy276.25\frz8.248\move(229,221,195,221,8,2469)}I'll be waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:18.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:19.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:21.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:24.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Won't you come with me to see the fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.23,0:18:27.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think positive things would come out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:33.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we're together, I'm sure you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:41.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! If it were at least finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:45.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,those idiots would understand at least a little\nhow wonderful our game is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.82,0:18:47.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:18.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:27.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is a copy of the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:32.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These past few days, you skipped\ncounseling without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:35.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's a complete violation of this contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:37.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"I'll be collecting that fine of one million yen."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:39.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! You were...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:41.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is what I could say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:46.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I was also keeping my house a secret from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:50.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I feel a little guilty about that. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:55.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As a result, I'll dispense with the fine this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:59.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Starting tomorrow, we'll do counseling\nas we did previously,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:02.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but you absolutely must come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:04.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you to decide things for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:19.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm glad you came back for me, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:23.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:38.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Glad to be home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:46.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H725255&\3c&H342314&\shad0\bord2\frx26\fry54\pos(267,120)\frz325.865}Mita House
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:20:59.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:03.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.02,0:21:06.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hello? Tatsuhiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:09.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah. Mom, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:14.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wanted to talk to you a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:17.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's sure a gloomy voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:19.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if she heard something\nabout the "Off" meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:25.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's with the gloomy voice?\NThat's not like you, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.81,0:21:28.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm feeling really well on my end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.62,0:21:30.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.15,0:21:33.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this? So, it's not about the "Off" meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:36.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tatsuhiro? Stay calm and listen, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:38.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:41.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The truth is, I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:45.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? I can't hear you very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.47,0:21:52.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:56.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's... It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:59.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H72AA7B&\3c&H000000&\shad0\bord2.3\fscx203.75\fscy201.25\pos(193,94)}Episode 14
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:59.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H45894E&\bord2.3\shad0\3c&H000000&\fscx202.5\fscy231.25\pos(187,221)}Welcome to Reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.98,0:22:00.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're joking, right, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:24.87,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Moshimo ashita kono sekai ga owaru to shite mo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:27.34,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Kimi no koto dakara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.34,0:22:31.81,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,"Sore nara sore de mo ii ka"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.81,0:22:36.55,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Sokkenai taido toru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:40.55,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Muri suru koto wa nai kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.55,0:22:42.86,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Tama ni de mo ii kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.86,0:22:48.96,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Kao wo agete kocchi wo mite yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:51.77,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Watashi wo mite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.77,0:22:55.44,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Chippoke na sekai na no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.44,0:23:00.57,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Naze darou kono ryoute ni wa ookisugiru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.57,0:23:04.18,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Hateshinai sekai na no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.18,0:23:08.72,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Naze darou kono ryoute ni wa chiisasugiru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.72,0:23:15.99,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Nee modokashii asa no hikari no naka de
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.12,0:23:21.53,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Kimi to waraitai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.41,0:23:33.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You gather companions and adventure together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.57,0:23:34.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You work too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.74,0:23:36.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I owe this to you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.78,0:23:39.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next episode,\N"Welcome to the Fantasy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.37,0:23:39.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFB94C&\3c&H000000&\shad0\bord2.3\pos(194,82)}Next Episode
